{"tid":202320,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"囚犯任上網！高手獄中自砌電腦, 隱藏天花偷駁網絡","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T13:43:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdfe5674c62b93c657c6dc477724b5e7cacc59f","tid":202320,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:54:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">囚犯任上網！高手獄中自砌電腦, 隱藏天花偷駁網絡<br />\n<a href=\"https://c6up.com/2017/04/13/self-built-computer-in-prison/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc6up.com%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2Fself-built-computer-in-prison%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a323e016\" target=\"_blank\">https://c6up.com/2017/04/13/self-built-computer-in-prison/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://c6upcom.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc6upcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2F124.jpg&h=52263b8e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n對於大部分囚犯來說，用手機或電腦上網都是不可能的事。不過在美國俄亥俄州一個監獄，就有高手囚犯成功自行「穿針引線」上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n事源監獄 IT 部門發現有連接設施網絡的裝置網絡流量超出上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，期後發現這部機已經運行超過 4 個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。經過足足 3 星期搜尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，終於在一間訓練室的天花板上面找到電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。調查後得知有囚犯秘密自行組合兩部電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，收藏在天花上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，再偷偷拉線佔用監獄的網絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://c6upcom.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc6upcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2F28.jpg&h=6a914592&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在電腦的硬碟裡面找到 Windows 伺服器、VPN、VOIP、無痕瀏覽器、防毒軟件等。亦有竊取密碼和電郵的工具，以及為數不少的成人內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。更加有製作毒品、炸藥、假信用卡等教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。製作電腦的囚犯用電腦和網絡來向其他囚犯售賣各種服務，例如透過網絡打電話。更加有進行各種詐騙，以後搜尋監獄的資料和通行權限。<br />\n<br />\n不過究竟他們是怎樣在獄中砌出兩部電腦？原來囚犯其中一個工作是幫助當地電子零件回收計劃。他們就是在途中偷走零件，重新組合後運到少人檢查的位置。放到天花板上，再自行拉電線和網絡線。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://c6upcom.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc6upcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2F37.jpg&h=a4ca437d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n來源: <a href=\"http://watchdog.ohio.gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwatchdog.ohio.gov&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c8693ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">watchdog.ohio.gov</a>"},{"pid":"7effee919bb44980d5cb8595f72fcd222a82b147","tid":202320,"uid":6386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a13612c90d7167f30605ffefaa921e8c162098","tid":202320,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"聰明"},{"pid":"576884a587db9fb24297475ab6b6ca1eac4a09c1","tid":202320,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"坐緊監 你問我答"},{"pid":"d09d55bd2226256811b4070a386d7bac8de17315","tid":202320,"uid":81308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"係咪連登仔